      <view class="info-title">小区:</view>
      <view class="info-detail">新龙城</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='message a'>
    <text class='iconfont icon-sheshi'></text>
    房屋设施
    <view>
      <view>1、房屋情况:三室两厅户型正采光好出行方便</view>
